description: Black soldier fly (maggot/larvae) is low in pathogen infection and contains antimicrobial peptide which makes maggot more valuable compared to other insects as feed. Bestico Dried Larvae is a product of black soldier fly by heating fresh larvae in a short time that still contains high protein and fat content. Dried Larvae triggers a positive behavioral response and higher feed intake at low inclusion rates. In addition to a rich and well-balanced protein and fatty acid content, dried larvae provides a wide range of interesting micronutrients.
benefit: More iron and sinc than lean meat, its calcium content is higher than milk, Essential amino acids
